About LiteSQL 
-------------

LiteSQL is a C++ library that provides an easy interface to sqlite3 database 
engine, light level of object persistence, object relation support, class-based
API for generating queries and iterator-like cursors.

See HTML documentation for details docs/html/index.html.

Project home page: http://litesql.sourceforge.net

Installation
------------
Create Makefiles with cmake 

cmake .

Then compile and install

make install

By Tero Laitinen <tero.laitinen@iki.fi>
